WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:05.660 --> 00:00:12.670
When it went on sale in 2008, the Cruze finally
provided Chevrolet a highly competitive model

00:00:12.670 --> 00:00:16.070
in the hotly contested compact sedan segment.

00:00:16.070 --> 00:00:23.930
Round 2 starts in 2016 with an all-new Cruze;
larger, lighter and faster with a more dynamic

00:00:23.930 --> 00:00:26.930
driving experience, according to Chevy.

00:00:26.930 --> 00:00:32.320
Now that the Malibu is getting bigger, the
Cruze has room to grow too, now nearly 3”

00:00:32.320 --> 00:00:36.100
longer affording more rear leg and knee room.

00:00:36.100 --> 00:00:42.920
A sleeker design with wind-cheating aerodynamics,
the new Cruze utilizes a lighter steel body

00:00:42.920 --> 00:00:49.950
and a new turbocharged engine with auto start/stop
to achieve an estimated 40mpg highway when

00:00:49.950 --> 00:00:54.070
paired with the available 6-speed automatic
transmission.2016 Chevrolet CruzeA 6-speed

00:00:54.070 --> 00:00:56.080
manual is standard.

00:00:56.080 --> 00:01:03.630
Until the new Diesel model arrives in 2017,
the sole engine is a 1.4-liter turbo-4 making

00:01:03.630 --> 00:01:09.000
153 horsepower and 177 pound-feet of torque.

00:01:09.000 --> 00:01:13.970
The increased output leads to a 0-to-60mph
time of 8.0-seconds, making it one of the

00:01:13.970 --> 00:01:16.300
quickest cars in the class.

00:01:16.300 --> 00:01:22.000
Technology fans will welcome the addition
of the all-new Chevy MyLink infotainment unit,

00:01:22.000 --> 00:01:28.280
now with Apple CarPlay and Android Auto – systems
that turn the center screen into an extension

00:01:28.280 --> 00:01:32.440
of your smartphone for easier, safer connectivity.

00:01:32.440 --> 00:01:36.070
Wireless phone charging is also new for 2016.

00:01:36.070 --> 00:01:43.740
And of course it’s offered with OnStar with
4G LTE and built-in Wi-Fi hotspot.A more sophisticated

00:01:43.740 --> 00:01:49.610
machine with premium offerings small car owners
now demand such as optional heated rear seats

00:01:49.610 --> 00:01:55.610
and advanced safety features, the 2016 Cruze
is offered in a new model range beginning

00:01:55.610 --> 00:02:03.190
with L, LS, LT and Premier as well as a more
expressive RS package with its own unique,

00:02:03.190 --> 00:02:08.590
sporty appearance.

